text: Andrey Fonseca (born 8 April 1993) is a Costa Rican cyclist. He rode at the cross-country event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Costa Rican male cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Costa Rica Category:Cyclists at the 2015 Pan American Games Category:Cyclists at the 2019 Pan American Games
